threads.title: 820-4924 missing PP5V_S3, PP3V3_S4 missing
threads.message:
Board had very small liquid damage on U7501, replaced just in case.
Got light on charger.

PP5V_S5 and PP3V3_S5 are present but S4/S3/... are missing.

P5VS4_EN at 0V
PM_SLP_S5_L at 0V, no pulse when toggle SMC_ONOFF_L

I am not good at this - any idea?

threads.title: 820-4924 missing PP5V_S3, PP3V3_S4 missing
threads.message: Exact voltage on PPBUS_G3H? PPVRTC_G3H present? Must have been liquid elsewhere besides U7501..
